{"tid":1016622,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣會用手抆鼻毛","createTime":"2019-02-11T00:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T10:01:16.000Z","uid":93991,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"20d48ab480c7de5e9fcef0e2415fc9581a203206","tid":1016622,"uid":93991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T00:25:52.000Z","msg":"我啲鼻毛長得好快 剪完無耐又長到突出黎 琴晚訓唔著手多多抆下又一條 抆下又一條 抆左成五六條 怡家透氣好似新鮮左 但有種空虛既感覺 連根拔起會唔會以後唔生返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcd3ff54e818e10bd6b8aae2943a65318a1bdb2","tid":1016622,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T00:29:47.000Z","msg":"放心，越抆越密，我抆到頂唔順轉返剪"},{"pid":"f3171f6c3b879b0bd55790e6846fc016a234efd6","tid":1016622,"uid":93991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T00:41:28.000Z","msg":"抆既感覺真係好爽 同剪無得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbe1e4ea069a5816c9275ce91da19cf82a16aa8","tid":1016622,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T00:43:34.000Z","msg":"上網睇西人啲剃鬍片<br />\n佢地會用臘紙去脫鼻毛<br />\n用綿花棒塞啲臘果去鼻窿<br />\n等佢乾左一抆就清晒啲鼻毛<br />\n睇到都覺得爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b756902fa8b36998bf5db8cce493cf3c2b6ac4c1","tid":1016622,"uid":28702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T00:48:56.000Z","msg":"我得閑就會抆,<br />\n每次抆都忍住唔打乞嚏好有挑戰感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773c2d057501c2368a05c86a587a261010e92d42","tid":1016622,"uid":1482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T01:02:55.000Z","msg":"正 有時痛到標眼水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc18f4d0abba07395dc8eb667c6c07231343a120","tid":1016622,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T01:38:22.000Z","msg":"鼻毛好粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b894d5a78c5d0f70bbef95ef978510ab728e1432","tid":1016622,"uid":13638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T01:39:25.000Z","msg":"用開日本果隻鼻毛蠟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5181b095c8d815c596f12c8e441f455a8fefbe8","tid":1016622,"uid":122867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T01:44:16.000Z","msg":"抆到D好粗嘅好有成功感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ddf2d5abcbc4325dfe2b8d1678e66d2f349294d","tid":1016622,"uid":139468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T01:53:51.000Z","msg":"鼻毛唔係有佢嘅作用㗎咩？<br />\n抆到無哂鼻毛咪會直接吸哂啲塵入肺？<br />\n<br />\n利申：用手抆鼻毛好撚爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw, 以下 copy from Wiki:<br />\n<br />\n某些人的毛較茂盛，甚至太長會突出鼻孔外，因此有剪鼻毛器的工具誕生。<br />\n<br />\n如果拔鼻毛，可能引起毛囊炎。因為鼻子離大腦神經近，毛囊炎嚴重的話細菌會侵犯腦部，引起腦膜炎。"},{"pid":"94b521ec2879d4efefba3d6f0e55255c06ce53c5","tid":1016622,"uid":24523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T06:29:11.000Z","msg":"特別長同硬嘅鼻毛就會用手抆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392f11b408bc316f0adcdc3cb9eb016619e15fa0","tid":1016622,"uid":93991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:01:16.000Z","msg":"有時唔係唔想剪 對住塊鏡剪極都剪唔到"}]}